item.title: [317] slayer tower autospawn npcs ids[317]
item.dc:creator: @PvP_Bobby PvP Bobby
item.description:
@PvP_Bobby wrote:

It wouldn’t take that long to be honest. Just make a command to spawn the npc and write to a text file based on autospawns.cfg works.

EX:
::npc XXX

FileOutputStream (i think) fos;
fos.write(npc id)
fos.write(player position)
fos.newLine();
fos.close;

something along those lines. Because the moderators and admins don’t like people to spoon-feed others I wouldn’t really call this subject a “help needed” subject. But if you are really keen against doing so – find a 317 that has those said spawns and just leech it from there.
